*NOTE*
THOSE OF YOU WHO WONDER HOW THE IDEA OF THE GRID IS PRESENTED TO TIP MAY
FIND OUT BY TAKING OUT THE SCIMITAR TO HUNT THE SNARK (SANS GRID). THIS
FILE WAS WRITTEN TO COMPLETE THE GAME IN THE SHORTEST NUMBER OF MOVES
POSSIBLE.